ActOffshore Health and Safety Act
SubjectOrder Fixing the Day on which this Order is published and December 31, 2014 as the Days on which Certain Sections of the Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing the day on which the Order is published in the Canada Gazette, Part II, as the day on which sections 45 and 84 of the OFFSHORE HEALTH AND SAFETY ACT come into force, and December 31, 2014, as the day on which sections 2 to 44, 46 to 83, 85 to 93, and 96 to 119 of the same Act, chapter 13 of the Statutes of Canada, 2014, come into force.
